{"tid":983930,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"[Apple 己死] HKEPC : Apple 新 iPhone XI Max 規格曝光","createTime":"2019-01-16T11:18:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-17T10:35:57.000Z","uid":51620,"like":7,"dislike":75,"uniUserReply":39,"replies":[{"pid":"44245d536f141f62457e559c9b19c41ad66dac9f","tid":983930,"uid":51620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-16T11:18:31.000Z","msg":"上週在網上流傳了疑似新一代 iPhone XI 的設計圖，該圖片不僅曝光了新 iPhone XI 的外型，同時渲染圖亦洩露了背面的鏡頭可能會由雙鏡頭改成 3 鏡頭配置，最新在內地又有另一個新消息傳出，曝光更多有關於新 iPhone XI Max 型號手機的規格，包括電池容量、顯示屏幕等資料。<br />\n<br />\n根據來自內地社交網絡微博上的消息稱，全新的 iPhone XI Max 將會加入了不少新的技術，當中後置的攝影鏡頭將會由廣角、超廣角及3倍長焦三鏡頭所組成，同時電池容量亦會有所提升，將會內建 4000mAh 電池，比 iPhone XS Max 增加 826mAh，同時亦將支援 15W 無線快速充電。<br />\n<br />\n消息亦提到，新的 iPhone XI Max 將會換成<strong>「更小的瀏海」</strong>設計，至於手機的顯示屏將具有 90-120Hz 的屏幕刷新率，相信會為喜愛手機遊戲的玩家帶來更佳的遊戲體驗。<br />\n<img src=\"https://file.hkepc.net/2019/01/source/16182413531948348489.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffile.hkepc.net%2F2019%2F01%2Fsource%2F16182413531948348489.jpg&h=c6cff966&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a6e6fde4343b3bb8b747b31e9d1a46579fb8782","tid":983930,"uid":51620,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-16T11:18:39.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.hkepc.com/17624/4000mAh_%E9%9B%BB%E6%B1%A090-120Hz_%E5%B1%8F%E5%B9%95%E6%94%AF%E6%8F%B4_15W_%E7%84%A1%E7%B7%9A%E5%BF%AB%E5%85%85_Apple_%E6%96%B0_iPhone_XI_Max_%E8%A6%8F%E6%A0%BC%E6%9B%9D%E5%85%89?fbclid=IwAR2j5veAQyrmBfy32mXxVyqIELFL4y7quYv9cKckV0XkWgb6BFIsoOc_KTs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkepc.com%2F17624%2F4000mAh_%25E9%259B%25BB%25E6%25B1%25A090-120Hz_%25E5%25B1%258F%25E5%25B9%2595%25E6%2594%25AF%25E6%258F%25B4_15W_%25E7%2584%25A1%25E7%25B7%259A%25E5%25BF%25AB%25E5%2585%2585_Apple_%25E6%2596%25B0_iPh